N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 ยง 630.1 - Purpose

State Regulations

This Part establishes procedures and standards for the
selection and administration of multipurpose service centers for displaced
homemakers in furtherance of the policy of this State as enunciated in article
23-B of the Labor Law. Notes
